{
  "stem": "15197.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, they had expectation of me to be something, a little bit higher than all the siblings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the relation was very, very close, as I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even when I was with the other family people, with an aunt, my mother's sisters, they always, always thought that I will be able to manage or to give advice, being younger.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was quite a good student, I would say always.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was among the first in the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And later on when-- before the war, when I start high school, my mother, being the practical one, thought that I should also know a trade and she sent me additional to old school to learn how to sew, to learn how to cut forms.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I would say that this maybe saved my life because later when it was formed-- when the German came in to Poland and the walking shops, labor shops, were created, I was able to get into one because of my knowing how to sew, how to cut, how to advise.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, not knowingly, she foresaw that this can be very useful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was useful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They died during the first World War.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't remember even one grandparent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, as I said, he was-- I remember that people used to call him [NON-ENGLISH], which means that he was once upon years I don't remember very religious.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later he turned around and he had more interest what was going on in the world and he became more a social democratic outlook of life he had.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was the way how he looked at it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would say that he was very much involved with what was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
